# .gitattributes — 统一换行符,避免跨平台噪声 diff
# Normalize line endings to avoid CRLF/LF churn across Windows ↔ macOS/Linux.

* text=auto eol=lf

# 必须保持 CRLF 的 Windows 脚本 / Windows scripts that must keep CRLF:
*.bat   text eol=crlf
*.cmd   text eol=crlf
# PowerShell 通常 LF 即可;如团队需要可改 crlf
*.ps1   text eol=lf

# 二进制文件不要做行尾转换 / never touch binaries:
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.gif   binary
*.pdf   binary
*.zip   binary
*.lockb binary
